# ====================================
# NOTES FOR REVIEWERS
# ====================================

# 1. All reviewers must check that changes follow the coding standards
# 2. Security team must verify no secrets are committed
# 3. Architecture changes require architecture-lead approval
# 4. Database changes require dba-lead approval
# 5. Production deployments require devops-team approval
# 6. Breaking changes require tech-lead approval and documentation updates